title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: When trying to export data from a table that is nested inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: When attempting to export data from the table within the grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from the table inside the grid cell should complete successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a table into one grid cell.
2. Insert another table into a different grid cell.
3. Try to export the data from the first table inside the grid cell.
4. Observe that an exception is thrown in this scenario.
